00:45:13.350 --> 00:45:14.400
with the other person.

00:45:14.400 --> 00:45:15.983
ERIC SCHMIDT: And
an interesting thing

00:45:15.983 --> 00:45:18.400
in the bizarre
negotiation in DC, things

00:45:18.400 --> 00:45:20.980
became so bad between
the people that one

00:45:20.980 --> 00:45:23.100
of the political leaders
