00:50:21.610 --> 00:50:23.720
ERIC SCHMIDT: You remember
from our discussions

00:50:23.720 --> 00:50:26.219
that the Chinese have a
censorship portal, which

00:50:26.219 --> 00:50:28.260
was known colloquially as
the great firewall that

00:50:28.260 --> 00:50:30.246
